lign=left class=m><span class=title> First Post.... a couple poems...</span><hr size=1> If you like, I have more at www.penitentman.com, but these are my latest.  I kind of like the Silverstein-esqueness of these...<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Hairshorts</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
Today I formed<br>
the grandest plan<br>
ever conceived<br>
by mortal man<br>
<br>
For in the summer<br>
I get so hot<br>
I don't want to wear<br>
these clothes I've bought<br>
<br>
And in the winter <br>
I get such a chill <br>
(as evidenced by my <br>
electricity bill) <br>
<br>
I need cover in summer <br>
but it can't be too warm <br>
and extra heat in the winter <br>
to weather the storm <br>
<br>
My plan, you see <br>
is just common sense <br>
considering the fact <br>
that my leg hair's so dense <br>
<br>
I'll shave off the hair <br>
from my knees to my toes <br>
thus saving myself <br>
from these seasonal woes <br>
<br>
In summer I'll run naked <br>
but covered &quot;down there&quot; <br>
with a well tended forest <br>
of curly brown hair <br>
<br>
The shavings, I'll use <br>
to line winter clothes <br>
though I will need some help... <br>
purhaps someone who sews <br>
<br>
Great things are invented <br>
by men of all sorts <br>
but it took a man of vision <br>
to invent these hair-shorts <br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> The Ace up My Sleeve</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
<br>
Alone I sit in my private place<br>
My pants around my knees<br>
When at the door I hear a knock<br>
And someone's deadened pleas.<br>
<br>
The thing they want is mine for now<br>
The ace that's up my sleeve.<br>
I say that it might be awhile<br>
And they drop down to their knees.<br>
<br>
They say that I must hurry now<br>
I say I'll take my time<br>
And that is when I realize<br>
The power is all mine.<br>
<br>
So here I sit in my private place<br>
My pants around my knees<br>
I think I'll flush the toilet once<br>
<br>
<br>
Just to be a tease. <br>
<br>
